# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Engagement data — this is a pentest tool. Keep real recon out of the repo.
# The bundled demo (public/sample-scan.xml, bridge-vault/demo-vault/) is kept;
# these patterns only catch scans/exports dropped at the repo root.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/scan*.xml
/*.creds
/creds*.csv
/creds*.txt
/vault/
/vaults/
